Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.91,0:01:00.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘿  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:00.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.63,0:01:13.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.63,0:01:13.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.01,0:01:14.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,觉得这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:14.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you like it?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.01,0:01:14.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:14.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.26,0:01:16.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是火箭飞船  这都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:16.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a rocket ship, duh
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.22,0:01:19.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们下面见  给你到里面逛逛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:19.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll meet you downstairs and show you around
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.51,0:01:22.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要用它来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:22.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:24.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(413,152)}月球
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.81,0:01:24.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去月球  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:24.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the moon, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.10,0:01:26.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,月球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:26.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The moon
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.19,0:01:26.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:26.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I go?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.23,0:01:28.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:28.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No way, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.69,0:01:31.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别是自从你弄坏了我直升机以后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:30.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,especially after your little mishap
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:31.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with my whirlybird
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:32.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715,576)}逝者安息
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.48,0:01:34.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再说你也坐不下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:34.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, there's not enough room for you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.99,0:01:36.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我占不了多大地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:36.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I don't take up that much space
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.28,0:01:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到没
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.45,0:01:40.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我塞得进去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:40.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can fit in here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.78,0:01:42.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:42.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cozy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.83,0:01:44.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这抽屉我要用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:44.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need that drawer
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.75,0:01:46.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:46.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, how about this
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.96,0:01:47.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:47.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or this
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.04,0:01:48.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:48.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or this?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.04,0:01:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  这可不是闹着玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, this isn't for fun--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.25,0:01:53.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到这个了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:53.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See this?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.05,0:01:54.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是科学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:54.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is science
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.67,0:01:55.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没时间嬉耍打闹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:55.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have time for fun and games
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.97,0:01:57.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也没时间处理偷渡分子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:57.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I don't have time for stowaways
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.05,0:01:58.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:58.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.84,0:02:00.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就把我关进禁闭室里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:00.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put me in the brig
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.01,0:02:01.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:01.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't mind
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.60,0:02:03.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是通风口  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:03.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the air bed, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.27,0:02:06.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我也要用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:06.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need that, too
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.43,0:02:07.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了  我可以去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:07.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, please, can I go?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.98,0:02:08.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:08.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.85,0:02:09.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:09.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.52,0:02:11.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:11.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.86,0:02:14.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以待在货舱里  只要你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:14.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,y'all can ride in the cargo hold if you just
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.11,0:02:15.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:15.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.65,0:02:16.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去月球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:16.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Going to the moon
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.32,0:02:20.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,月球旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:20.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Moonride
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过这回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But this time
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么都不要碰  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just don't touch anything, okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.79,0:02:25.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看这气枪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:25.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at that popgun
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.08,0:02:27.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是要去月球抓外星人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:27.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are we going to go hunting aliens on the moon?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吵  傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, hush, silly
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是用来采集月球岩石的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is for harvesting moon rocks
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等你石头玩够了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When you're done playing with rocks
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.34,0:02:37.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也可以用那玩意来抓外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:37.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you could use that for some serious alien hunting
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.59,0:02:38.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:38.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aliens?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.59,0:02:39.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是傻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:39.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you nuts?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去过月球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been to the moon
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没有外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There are no aliens
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.31,0:02:46.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么能这么幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:46.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can you be so naive?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.97,0:02:48.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,周围到处都是证据
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:48.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's evidence all around us
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.81,0:02:50.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要怎么解释亚特兰蒂斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:50.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you explain Atlantis
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.81,0:02:51.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,翘头发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:51.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cowlicks
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.73,0:02:52.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,99分商店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:52.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,99-cent stores?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.31,0:02:54.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有怎么解释海草田里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:54.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And how about those mysterious circles
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一夜之间冒出来的怪圈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that pop up in kelp fields overnight?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.32,0:02:58.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:58.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's one now
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.32,0:03:01.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你对太空一窍不通
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:01.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you don't know the first thing about outer space
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.57,0:03:03.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在快回家睡觉去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:03.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now go home and get some shuteye
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天一早就过来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be here tomorrow at the crack of dawn
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别老是想什么外星人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and leave your crazy alien notions behind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:12.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1029,952)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.14,0:03:24.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:24.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry up
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样应该就成了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This ought to do the trick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hiya, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没看出来我在睡觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you see I'm sleeping here?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.23,0:03:37.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听说你明天就要去月球旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:37.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I know you're going on that moon trip tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想给你带份东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I just wanted to bring you something
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.44,0:03:40.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:40.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A present?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.53,0:03:43.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:43.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.91,0:03:47.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪的火箭能防外星人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:47.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is Sandy's rocket alien-proof?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.33,0:03:49.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没有外星人  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:49.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There are no aliens, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不信问珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just ask Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那看来你就用不着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you won't be needing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去月球时带上这个防外星人喷雾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this alien repellent for your trip
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,防外星人喷雾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alien repellent?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.92,0:03:57.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:57.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me see that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:01.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(937,176)}驱外星人
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全新款驱外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"New alien-out
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.67,0:04:00.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,窗户防护
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:00.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Window Protectant
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.84,0:04:01.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无法防小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:01.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Does not stop burglars"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你说得对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you're right, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好去给窗户都喷一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We better go spray those windows
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.60,0:04:09.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看它有多大  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:09.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look how big it is, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常厉害  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's pretty impressive, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.52,0:04:12.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:12.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.77,0:04:14.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们只是来这喷窗户的  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:14.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're just here to spray the windows, Patrick
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:19.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1093,906)}开
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说要怎样才能进去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you think we get inside?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.11,0:04:19.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:19.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.90,0:04:20.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们只是来这喷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:20.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're just spraying the
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.07,0:04:22.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,窗户的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:22.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,windows
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我打开了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I opened it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.66,0:04:25.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:25.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy sea cow, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这肯定就是控制室了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This must be the control room
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  什么都不要乱碰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just don't touch anything
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  我要赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm winning
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, cut that out
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, come on
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.38,0:04:44.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能在里面到处乱晃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:44.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't hang around in here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是珊迪的大火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is Sandy's big rocket
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.55,0:04:49.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是什么游乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:49.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not some kind of fun house
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Winner
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.23,0:04:53.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,耶  高分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:53.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, high score
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  话说那是什么游戏来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, what game was that, anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道  不过来看看这是干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but let's see what this does
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  好像不该
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I don't think we should
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好喜欢火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like rockets
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来  再来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More, more
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.70,0:05:07.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:07.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, one more
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's enough
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.34,0:05:21.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:21.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.26,0:05:24.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  这个好像可以启动火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:24.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, I think this one starts it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去太空旅行的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the space traveler here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.76,0:05:28.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚好知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:28.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I happen to know that
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个启动按钮就在这
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that particular button is right over here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们启动火箭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've started the rocket
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.37,0:05:52.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,撑住  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:52.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hang on, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不坠落了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We stopped falling
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看  我们上太空了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, we're in space now
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.30,0:06:10.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁来拉我下来上去之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:10.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somebody get me down or up, or something
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  瞧好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, watch this
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把牙膏挤到我花生酱里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got your toothpaste in my peanut butter
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.44,0:06:28.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我可以这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:28.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I can do this
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.91,0:06:36.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁又把重力打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:36.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who turned the heavy back on?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们肯定要着陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We must be landing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.50,0:06:43.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有时候海绵宝宝就是傻得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:41.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes that SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is as dumb as a sack of peanuts
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看起来跟家好像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It sure looks a lot like home
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.85,0:07:01.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  是小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:01.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, look, it's Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.48,0:07:03.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来  小蜗小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:03.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come here, Gary, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.40,0:07:03.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:03.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要靠近它  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't go near him, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看不出来这都是诡计吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you see this is all a trick?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.36,0:07:10.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外星人在把我们的记忆投射到环境里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The aliens are projecting our memories
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:10.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,onto the environment
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是要迷惑我们  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're trying to confuse us, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.49,0:07:13.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你是想说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:13.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you mean to say
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们取出了我们想的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they've taken what we thought we think
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.58,0:07:16.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我们想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:16.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and make us think
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们一直在想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we thought our thoughts we've been thinking
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们想的想法的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,our thoughts we think we thought?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.79,0:07:20.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,心里想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:20.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We think?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.87,0:07:23.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我是不会上当的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:23.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, but I'm not going to fall for it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.13,0:07:28.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到它了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:28.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got him, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪会不会很骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Won't Sandy be proud?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.93,0:07:31.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:31.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.63,0:07:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都忘了她了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot all about her
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们偷她火箭  她会讨厌我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's going to hate us for stealing her rocket
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但等我把外星人带给她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But won't she feel silly
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.81,0:07:38.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她会不会觉得自己傻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:38.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I bring her back a real live alien?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.98,0:07:39.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她会爱上我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:39.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She'll love me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.69,0:07:41.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:41.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人多力量大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The more the merrier
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alien hunting
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘘  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shh, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别暴露抓他们的动机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't let them know we're on to them
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  抓外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, alien hunting--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.24,0:07:53.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也在电视上看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:53.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saw that on TV, too
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.57,0:07:58.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  顺便来看下老朋友章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:58.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, let's drop in on our old pal Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.20,0:07:59.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看他想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:07:59.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and see what he's up to
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.45,0:08:01.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确保气枪的气打好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:01.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make sure your gun is pumped
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at it, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's disgusting
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.22,0:08:15.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:15.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grandma
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凑近看更丑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's even uglier up close
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.81,0:08:24.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始分析吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:24.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's begin the analysis
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.44,0:08:29.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:29.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得我快要吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'm going to be sick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你知道这是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, do you know what this thing is?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.62,0:08:40.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,臭臭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:40.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stinky
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.87,0:08:43.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  是卵囊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:43.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it's an egg sac
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看胚胎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's look at the embryo
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Twins
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.42,0:08:53.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉用语不当
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:53.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon my French
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把这东西从我身上弄下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but get this thing off me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星和海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick and SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚出我的卧室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get out of my bedroom
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.73,0:09:07.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放下我的爪子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:07.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and give me back my tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.06,0:09:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's awake
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.52,0:09:10.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来抓住这个小骗子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:10.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's capture the little phony
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离我远点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好啊  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, there, lads
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.00,0:09:28.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在扮海盗是不是有点晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:28.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up a bit late to be playing pirate, aren't ye?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.09,0:09:32.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:32.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, don't shoot
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧好吧  开枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, shoot me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是别拿走我的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but don't take me money
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.55,0:09:39.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不想要你的钱  月球人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:39.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't want your money, moon man
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.35,0:09:45.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看他们在里面蠕动的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:45.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at them squirming around in there
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gross
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.94,0:09:50.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外星人还有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:50.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, plenty more where those came from
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(595,254)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  这么晚来这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what are you doing here so late?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管这是干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever this is
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.58,0:10:06.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都要记在你档案里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:06.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's going on your permanent record
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.30,0:10:15.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:15.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please let me out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.89,0:10:24.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我觉得可能要再跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:24.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I think we might have to make a second trip
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没时间搞那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no time for that--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用力推
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just push harder
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你们在搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what are y'all doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.19,0:10:31.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我放任你们两秒钟不管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:31.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't turn my back on you for two seconds
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.86,0:10:34.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就闯了一大堆的祸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:34.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without you causing a whole mess of trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, look at you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.44,0:10:37.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把你朋友跟邻居全塞袋子里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:37.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bagging up all your friends and neighbors
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.03,0:10:40.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就好像有新鲜的山核桃熏香肠似的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just like there was a fresh crop
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of hickory-smoked sausages
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.61,0:10:44.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们把我的科学小实验搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:42.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You done turned my little science experiment
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:44.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,into a disaster
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们应该为自己感到羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two ought to be ashamed of yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.58,0:10:48.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别骗人了  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:48.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice try, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.00,0:10:52.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者该不该说是  外星小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:52.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or should I say, miss alien pants?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aliens?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.30,0:10:56.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是你们的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:56.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that what this is about?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是月球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't the moon
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还在裤头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're still in Bikini Bo --
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.51,0:11:04.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟你说  谁都不能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:04.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just goes to show you, you can't trust anyone
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.64,0:11:10.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你一直都是个外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:10.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, you were an alien all the time
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.85,0:11:12.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而你却从来不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:12.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you didn't even tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't even know
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.77,0:11:14.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:14.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.52,0:11:15.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我该抓你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:15.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I got you now
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.57,0:11:19.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是抓不到我的  只有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:19.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's not you that's got me, it's
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.57,0:11:23.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我抓我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:23.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me that's got me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.33,0:11:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  等不及要看到珊迪的表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, I can't wait to see the look on Sandy's face
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.04,0:11:35.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:35.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, I'm back
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村看着好不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom sure looks different
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.05,0:11:46.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我们外星人想跟你说句话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:46.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, we aliens would like a word with you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:53.23,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(482,520)}吱吱叫的靴子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:55.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(287,306)\frz11.86}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:55.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz11.86\pos(403,650)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:58.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:58.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz11.86\pos(477,282)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:01.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz11.86\pos(279,294)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:01.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(443,634)\frz16.64}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:01.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.07,0:12:06.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍是我女儿  我要烦死你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:06.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl is my daughter, I'll spit in your eye
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.83,0:12:10.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍是头鲸鱼  今天是她生日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:10.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl's a whale, and it's her birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的表演  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the show, dad
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在能开礼物了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now can we open the presents?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我亲爱的小沙丁鱼的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Presents for me darling little sardine
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.72,0:12:23.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:23.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是什么  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, daddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.35,0:12:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该不会是我朋友都在穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be those totally hip new flipper slippers
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.10,0:12:31.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全新脚蹼鞋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:31.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all my friends are wearing
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都可想要了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone wants them
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.98,0:12:36.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:36.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It might be
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.23,0:12:39.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:39.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.11,0:12:41.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用不着这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:41.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.65,0:12:42.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:42.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, dad
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.95,0:12:44.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就用不着送这礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:44.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You really shouldn't have
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.91,0:12:50.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  这双可是全场最好的钓鱼靴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:50.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl, those are the finest fishing boots available
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.54,0:12:52.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸  你毁了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:52.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dad, you ruined me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.83,0:12:56.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是砍价买的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:56.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I got them for a bargain
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:02.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(378.526,372)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.63,0:13:03.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:03.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.76,0:13:06.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我整整花了两块钱买了这靴子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:06.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I spent two whole dollars on these boots
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.26,0:13:07.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在这玩意甩不开了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:07.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now I'm stuck with them
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我能领工资吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, can I get my paycheck?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongeboy-me-bob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.73,0:13:13.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进请进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:13.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come in, come in
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.77,0:13:14.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到这来  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:14.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right this way, laddie
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐哪都行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have a seat anywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.56,0:13:21.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是别坐上这双美丽无价的靴子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:21.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but not on these beautiful, priceless boots
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你想领工资
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you want your pay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.78,0:13:26.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老板  我看不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:26.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sir, I can't see you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.95,0:13:27.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,靴子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:27.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The boots
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.03,0:13:28.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:28.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are in
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.62,0:13:29.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,视线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:29.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the way
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.95,0:13:30.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挡视线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:30.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In the way?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.16,0:13:33.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这双靴子从来就没离开过我的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:33.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These boots never leave my sight
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.12,0:13:37.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我手上既昂贵又珍贵的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:34.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are the most expensive
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:37.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and prized possessions I own
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.21,0:13:38.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:38.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.13,0:13:39.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:39.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.84,0:13:41.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这靴子跟一般的靴子没区别
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:41.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They look just like any old ordinary boots
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.59,0:13:43.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一般的靴子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:43.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ordinary boots?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.88,0:13:47.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是绝无仅有的正式煎炸厨师靴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:47.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are the only official fry cook boots
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.43,0:13:50.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有全世界最好的煎炸厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:50.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only the finest fry cooks in the world
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.10,0:13:52.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才可以穿上  这是传统
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:52.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are permitted to wear them, part of a tradition
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.93,0:13:55.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这双靴子是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:55.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And these boots were given to me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.18,0:13:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一位海底最有名的煎炸厨师给的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by the most famous fry cook in the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.56,0:13:59.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:13:59.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是谁不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, his name is not important
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.78,0:14:04.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正他很有名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:04.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But he was famous
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  别管那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, don't you worry
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.57,0:14:08.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要靴子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:08.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want those boots
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.07,0:14:12.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉小子  这靴子实在太珍贵了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:12.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, son, these boots are far too valuable
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.70,0:14:14.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:14.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我拿蟹堡王的工资抵怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What if I give you my Krusty Krab paycheck?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,工资
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Paycheck
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.25,0:14:20.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成交
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:20.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got a deal
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.17,0:14:22.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我免费粉刷蟹堡王怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:22.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what if I paint the Krusty Krab for free?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.46,0:14:23.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成交
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:23.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got a deal
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.46,0:14:25.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还要免费送够一年用的薯条油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:25.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'll throw in a year's supply of French fry oil
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.42,0:14:26.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:26.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on there, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.55,0:14:29.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要害我心脏病发作了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:29.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to give me a heart attack
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.14,0:14:33.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都成交
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:33.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got yourself a deal
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喜欢我的新靴子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you like my new boots?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.33,0:14:54.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很酷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:54.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty cool, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.54,0:14:56.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我是正式煎炸厨师了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:56.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm an official fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.10,0:15:18.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吱吱叫的声音要害我疯掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:18.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That squeaking is going to drive us all crazy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡说八道  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nonsense, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.44,0:15:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吱吱叫的声音在我听来就是钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That squeaking is money to my ears
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.77,0:15:24.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:24.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, music
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.95,0:15:32.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:32.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ten
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.61,0:15:33.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二十
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:33.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Twenty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.28,0:15:33.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三十
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:33.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thirty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.87,0:15:34.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四十
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:34.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.87,0:15:36.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:36.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁在那
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.12,0:15:43.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续数钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:43.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back to counting me money
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.33,0:15:44.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:44.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.92,0:15:45.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:45.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.79,0:15:46.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:46.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.67,0:15:47.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:47.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Four
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.71,0:15:48.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:48.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Five
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那到底是什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the barnacle is that, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.91,0:16:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Careful
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.65,0:16:53.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,昨晚是我度过的最难熬的一晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:53.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was the worst night I ever weathered
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(503,428)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.24,0:16:56.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少我上班还能享受清静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:56.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least I'll have some peace and quiet at work
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch it, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要度我的假去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm taking my vacation now
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mr. Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.79,0:17:07.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也受不了世界最好煎炸厨师了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:07.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take the world's greatest fry cook anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一星期后再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll see you in a week
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.17,0:17:12.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那煎炸厨师在帮我发大财
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:12.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That fry cook is making me a fortune
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.21,0:17:13.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:13.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What could be the problem?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘿  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.39,0:17:19.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:19.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.31,0:17:23.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:23.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到你还在穿这双靴子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,see you're still wearing them boots
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.73,0:17:26.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:26.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.81,0:17:27.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:27.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love them
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.73,0:17:30.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全世界最好的厨师能这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:30.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could the world's greatest fry cook do this?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.45,0:17:36.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:36.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.07,0:17:36.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:36.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.82,0:17:37.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:37.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他还会不会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or could he do this?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.87,0:17:40.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:40.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:45.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(459,508)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,瞧好了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And watch this, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.62,0:17:47.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能为你点餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:47.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I take your order?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我要来份蟹堡特餐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll have the Krusty special
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.88,0:17:50.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:50.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.13,0:17:52.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做好我会吱一声的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:52.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will squeak when it's ready
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好的厨师能这样吗  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could the greatest fry cook do that, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.76,0:17:56.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:56.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看这个  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And look at this, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.89,0:18:02.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:02.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.85,0:18:11.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:11.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.28,0:18:14.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得去办公室一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:14.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to go to my office
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.61,0:18:19.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是听得到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:19.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can still hear it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是能透过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's still coming through
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.95,0:18:27.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可恶的吱吱叫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:27.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The infernal squeak
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.58,0:18:30.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这靴子必须消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:30.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those boots have got to go
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来片阿司匹林
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I need an aspirin
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.59,0:18:39.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  这双靴子改变了我的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:39.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, these boots have changed my life
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:41.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(227,794)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不脱掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm never taking them off
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.89,0:18:42.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:42.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, Gary
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:17.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(399,370)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.63,0:19:17.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安静的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:17.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quiet money
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.80,0:19:21.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既有宁静又有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:21.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Silence and money
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  我的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, my boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.26,0:19:27.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我好对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:27.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.18,0:19:28.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:28.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.43,0:19:30.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:30.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.31,0:19:31.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:31.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay, son
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.77,0:19:34.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  很有事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:34.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it's not okay
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.61,0:19:36.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把靴子丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:36.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost the boots
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.94,0:19:38.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你珍贵的靴子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:38.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your valuable boots
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's my fault
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我让你失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I let you down
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.57,0:19:44.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:44.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.03,0:19:47.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:47.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.70,0:19:48.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别哭  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:48.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.87,0:19:50.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这又不是世界末日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:50.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not the end of the world
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好  别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, don't cry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.21,0:19:55.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有双
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:55.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got some, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有双神奇烤箱手套
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some magic oven mitts
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.97,0:20:03.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那又不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:03.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're not the same
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were right--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.68,0:20:08.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还不配穿上那双神圣靴子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:08.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wasn't ready for those blessed boots
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.69,0:20:12.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可怜的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:12.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor lad
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.61,0:20:17.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:17.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.57,0:20:18.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是我干的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:18.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.99,0:20:21.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能为你服务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:21.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I help you?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我要点餐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm ready to order
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.61,0:20:24.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:24.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What'll you have?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.74,0:20:25.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:25.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take a
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.66,0:20:28.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:28.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.95,0:20:30.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说我要点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:30.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said I'll take a
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听到他点的菜了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I heard his order, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.54,0:20:35.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说他要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:35.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He said he wants
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.92,0:20:37.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:37.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.59,0:20:38.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:38.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And a
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.47,0:20:45.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:45.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:50.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1125,862)}吱吱吱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(731,808)}吱吱吱
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.43,0:20:53.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是我写的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:53.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't write that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:56.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(787,766)}吱吱吱
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.48,0:21:01.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁说的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:01.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.40,0:21:04.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:04.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.20,0:21:08.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全世界最好的煎炸厨师能这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:08.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could the world's greatest fry cook do this?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.20,0:21:15.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:15.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.13,0:21:20.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:20.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you hear it?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.34,0:21:22.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  是我干的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:22.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.26,0:21:23.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我干的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:23.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.26,0:21:25.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把靴子拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:25.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I took the boots
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.01,0:21:28.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,靴子就在这地板底下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:28.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're here under the floorboard
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.72,0:21:31.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你消停消停吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:31.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, please, make it stop
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.26,0:21:34.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是这丑的要命的靴子吱吱叫声害的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:34.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the squeaking of the hideous boots
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.27,0:21:37.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:37.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.65,0:21:41.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也受不了那个可恶的吱吱叫声了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:41.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I can't take the infernal squeaking no more
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.25,0:21:56.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,事成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:56.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The deed is done
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.50,0:21:59.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么在吃我靴子  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:21:59.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did you eat my boots, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.46,0:22:01.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为小子  你用不着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:01.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because, lad, you didn't need them
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.59,0:22:03.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是因为靴子  是因为贵重物品
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:03.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not the boots, it's the bootee
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.05,0:22:07.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说靴子背后的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:07.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean the person in the boots
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.51,0:22:09.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是个很棒的煎炸厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:09.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a great fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真这么觉得吗  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You really think so, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.18,0:22:12.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:12.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do, son
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.22,0:22:13.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我欠你的工资
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:13.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your paycheck I owe you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.22,0:22:15.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外加奖金
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:15.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,plus a bonus
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.14,0:22:19.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  还是只给工资好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:19.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, there's your paycheck anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.27,0:22:21.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要休个假
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:21.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.27,0:22:23.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:23.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.90,0:22:28.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离开裤头村一周时间
